石分分鐘 一睇就知好黃（低 colour)<br />\n<br />\n你上網做下功課先去 唔係比人水左 真係無謂<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：啱啱求完婚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打去邊買??</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我唔開名啦<br />\n廢事好似打手咁<br />\n<br />\n其實樓上巴打講得啱，上網了解多d 先<br />\n而家有d 網 放哂d 石上網 有埋gia 証書<br />\n你可睇果d 了解下究竟係咩黎先去鋪頭睇<br />\n你先唔會比人帶住黎傾囉"},{"pid":"bace64f05d81e50820a3e9e0a72dc04f32c9f675","tid":36853,"uid":310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:37:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>iprimo算唔算一線?<br />\n買左粒0.3 if 3皮好肉赤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以巴打budget 想買咁大粒<br />\niprimo 一定無可能做到"},{"pid":"e249bb572863c96cdad7cad0ad9fcbb4c113e0ee","tid":36853,"uid":49978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:44:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>iprimo算唔算一線?<br />\n買左粒0.3 if 3皮好肉赤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以巴打budget 想買咁大粒<br />\niprimo 一定無可能做到</blockquote><br />\n點錯相?<br />\n我岩岩入離問<br />\n我本身睇1卡,覺得好撚大,太俗唔靚<br />\n再睇半卡, 拎左粒0.3 if 同0.5 vvs <br />\n一睇已經分到分別<br />\n但個價可以差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實iprimo個價係咪同tiffany.卡地那已經一樣?"},{"pid":"b61b91bc03f84dc984ba368b0e8d07f66d797d2f","tid":36853,"uid":35651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:44:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"79c6495183fecf29ca30b70aed06a96aa80afe8e","tid":36853,"uid":52794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:46:40.000Z","msg":"搵我買 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d7048c45171bb9271041be188654d085d82cfa7","tid":36853,"uid":27991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:50:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啱呀<br />\n你揀90幾份 肉眼睇大細唔會爭太遠<br />\n但你要執著要1卡 咁個價都會跳一級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但0.90 份難搵, 唔多貨</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實行內大把貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n哥哥仔，我都係呢行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8825594abad7fd7bf6300364c93e2b02ae7c6bd7","tid":36853,"uid":310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:50:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>iprimo算唔算一線?<br />\n買左粒0.3 if 3皮好肉赤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以巴打budget 想買咁大粒<br />\niprimo 一定無可能做到</blockquote><br />\n點錯相?<br />\n我岩岩入離問<br />\n我本身睇1卡,覺得好撚大,太俗唔靚<br />\n再睇半卡, 拎左粒0.3 if 同0.5 vvs <br />\n一睇已經分到分別<br />\n但個價可以差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實iprimo個價係咪同tiffany.卡地那已經一樣?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實iprimo 呢d 一線 d 石 係偏貴"},{"pid":"cf65166644c33df71c62be10d7ccbacaed58c4b4","tid":36853,"uid":16198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:50:17.000Z","msg":"留名學野"},{"pid":"0f5adf8a0568873fe9dba373a0530d3ecdc9d8cb","tid":36853,"uid":48623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:50:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴打<br />\n鑽石既價錢 係由一堆標準 去定<br />\n當然 大細其中一樣啦<br />\n仲有 colour , cutting 係咪3個excellent, 淨度等等 去決定 <br />\n你呢個budget 買1 卡 所有grade 應該都係好低<br />\n粒石分分鐘 一睇就知好黃（低 colour)<br />\n<br />\n你上網做下功課先去 唔係比人水左 真係無謂<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：啱啱求完婚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打去邊買??</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我唔開名啦<br />\n廢事好似打手咁<br />\n<br />\n其實樓上巴打講得啱，上網了解多d 先<br />\n而家有d 網 放哂d 石上網 有埋gia 証書<br />\n你可睇果d 了解下究竟係咩黎先去鋪頭睇<br />\n你先唔會比人帶住黎傾囉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n樓上鋪平好多，自己刨下高登，之前有個叫「星期一」既巴打講好多，我當年求婚買石都有請教過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。"},{"pid":"3c8fa98b07df78ff6e39fa37ddc1771c4bd9316c","tid":36853,"uid":58671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:53:03.000Z","msg":"好奇問下求婚戒點解會唔選擇買大brand？"},{"pid":"2ac6f44e8325c5d371472e4a7c4f6d391406f994","tid":36853,"uid":310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:55:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好奇問下求婚戒點解會唔選擇買大brand？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實睇你點諗<br />\n大brand 個戒指款好靚 但石偏貴<br />\n樓上鋪 石係平好多 但d 戒指托既款好簡單 四爪 六爪等等<br />\n<br />\n如果我無限budget 一定去大brand 啦<br />\n有限budget 下 又唔想粒石細 只好去樓上鋪<br />\n<br />\n呢個係我睇法囉"},{"pid":"e8ad330af8a03c2213bbd0ab28df9ff2037d48fb","tid":36853,"uid":49978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:55:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>iprimo算唔算一線?<br />\n買左粒0.3 if 3皮好肉赤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以巴打budget 想買咁大粒<br />\niprimo 一定無可能做到</blockquote><br />\n點錯相?<br />\n我岩岩入離問<br />\n我本身睇1卡,覺得好撚大,太俗唔靚<br />\n再睇半卡, 拎左粒0.3 if 同0.5 vvs <br />\n一睇已經分到分別<br />\n但個價可以差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實iprimo個價係咪同tiffany.卡地那已經一樣?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實iprimo 呢d 一線 d 石 係偏貴</blockquote><br />\n其我唔識佢係咪一線叫一線,但又急買, 朋友介紹就去左, 其實佢算唔算一線?<br />\n<br />\n買完事後睇番樓上舖d價,粒石直情成幾倍價錢<br />\n但問親都話冇, 係咪呢類貨源好少?"},{"pid":"21c48ffc3fcb1cbc859819f7971981311d08d9e4","tid":36853,"uid":27991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:55:47.000Z","msg":"睇budget 買啦<br />\n想碌卡分期就去大舖, 想平既就去細舖<br />\n講真太多技術野, 普通街客講完都未必明<br />\n<br />\n而且VS 已經足夠, 除非女方真係超級想要VVS 以上<br />\n否則真係浪費金錢"},{"pid":"6de5b7953fd89e8de0bde31109d92f1da40d9647","tid":36853,"uid":27991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:56:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n點錯相?<br />\n我岩岩入離問<br />\n我本身睇1卡,覺得好撚大,太俗唔靚<br />\n再睇半卡, 拎左粒0.3 if 同0.5 vvs <br />\n一睇已經分到分別<br />\n但個價可以差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實iprimo個價係咪同tiffany.卡地那已經一樣?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實iprimo 呢d 一線 d 石 係偏貴</blockquote><br />\n其我唔識佢係咪一線叫一線,但又急買, 朋友介紹就去左, 其實佢算唔算一線?<br />\n<br />\n買完事後睇番樓上舖d價,粒石直情成幾倍價錢<br />\n但問親都話冇, 係咪呢類貨源好少?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能係 iprimo 無入"},{"pid":"1b85c80bd108a0c21caa4125b2b53937b3a072ec","tid":36853,"uid":51924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T07:01:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好奇問下求婚戒點解會唔選擇買大brand？</blockquote><br />\n食水深 反正都係買gia"},{"pid":"c0474894a79430addbde4c942be5a3336c5fe313","tid":36853,"uid":27964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T07:01:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但0.90 份難搵, 唔多貨</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實行內大把貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n哥哥仔，我都係呢行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你係 賣石? 加工批發? 珠寶零售?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ca26ff0c2a7ec063069e1bbd0cf739ddd985eea","tid":36853,"uid":49978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T07:02:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n點錯相?<br />\n我岩岩入離問<br />\n我本身睇1卡,覺得好撚大,太俗唔靚<br />\n再睇半卡, 拎左粒0.3 if 同0.5 vvs <br />\n一睇已經分到分別<br />\n但個價可以差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實iprimo個價係咪同tiffany.卡地那已經一樣?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實iprimo 呢d 一線 d 石 係偏貴</blockquote><br />\n其我唔識佢係咪一線叫一線,但又急買, 朋友介紹就去左, 其實佢算唔算一線?<br />\n<br />\n買完事後睇番樓上舖d價,粒石直情成幾倍價錢<br />\n但問親都話冇, 係咪呢類貨源好少?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能係 iprimo 無入</blockquote><br />\n我就係iprimo入左, 事後問d樓上舖都係話賣左冇貨, 叫你睇第2d咁"},{"pid":"e028bc6a91d5f38cb5d9b0b8d9561eae0fd36aa7","tid":36853,"uid":27991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T07:04:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好奇問下求婚戒點解會唔選擇買大brand？</blockquote><br />\n食水深 反正都係買gia</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n反而我覺得 Tiffany 真係搵笨"},{"pid":"e716cc35c0a24224aa7cc3c92e6d808a6a31a9b4","tid":36853,"uid":11497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T0